description:
Draft Resource Management Plan and Environmental Impact Statement, published December 2012
Open to oil and gas leasing, BLM land, alternative C, dissolved to calculate acres, erased closed areas from RMP_BLM land to determine open areas. 

Theme: No leasing (to oil and gas) 
Description: Areas open oil and gas leasing under the Resource Management Plan revision by alternative. Everywhere not closed to oil and gas in the GJFO RMP planning area is designated as open 
Vintage: April 2012. 
Source: Data was derived from GJFO GIS data 
Capture Methodology: Copy/Paste from other RMP designated areas. 
Steward: Doug Diekman, GIS Specialist 970-244-3087
Attribute: See Entity Attribute for further details. 
Reliability: As per GJFO GIS data. 
Intended use: Cartographic use for display of public lands included in plan revision. 
Quality Control: GJFO GIS staff. 
Projection: UTM zone 13, Datum NAD 1983, Spheroid Clark 1866 
Agency Contact: Doug Diekman, GIS Specialist 970-244-3087
